wiki.content:
"Eh, Eh (Nothing Else I Can Say)" is a pop song recorded by American singer-songwriter Lady Gaga from her debut album The Fame. It has been announced as the third single in Australia, New Zealand, France and Switzerland. It received promotion in Australia and New Zealand, due to an increase in radio play but was not as successful as her previous singles reaching only fifteen in Australia and nine in New Zealand. It has been announced as the 4th single in The Netherlands. A human-beatbox version was performed live at the Cherrytree Studios and released on Lady Gaga's first EP, The Cherrytree Sessions.
